我喜欢的生活方式。当我表示想要待在欧洲的时候，我的经纪人很是震惊”， “假如好莱坞会给我带来很多，当然我不会不要，但是我只是不想在那里生活。”<ref>{{cite news   | last = [[Algemeen_Nederlands_Persbureau|ANP]]   | title = Carice van Houten wordt ongelukkig van Hollywood   | work = [[nu.nl|nu.nl]]   | language = nl   | date = 2007-07-05   | url = http://www.nu.nl/news/1208156/61/Carice_van_Houten_wordt_ongelukkig_van_Hollywood.html   | accessdate = 2007-07-05   | archive-date = 2008-09-21   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080921055116/http://www.nu.nl/news/1208156/61/Carice_van_Houten_wordt_ongelukkig_van_Hollywood.html   | dead-url = yes   }}</ref>

